{"pageProps":{"news":{"_id":"605e2ead14f2894457a29cdd","title":"新生报到","author":"","digest":"之前和将要到巴村的伙伴们分享了行前准备，这次提供关于新生报到的注意事项，大家有任何想要知道了解的欢迎回复，希望能为大家带来更多的信息有所帮助","content":"<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:Arial\">1.<span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px\">  </span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px\">报到以及注册</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Arial\">Orientation</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:24px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial\">Orientation</span>会持续一周左右的时间，就是帮助大家熟悉学校环境，尽快融入校园生活。一般有国际学生<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">orientation</span>，研究生院和各个院系的。国际学生<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">oriention</span>的时候请带齐所有证件，包括护照<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">I20</span>等，<strong>还有入境的</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:Arial\">I94</span></strong><strong>也很重要</strong>（<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">http://www.cbp.gov/I94</span>），因为要填写一系列的表格，很多证件号码你一定不记得。填写的表格包括<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">W4</span>和<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">workingpermit</span>的申请表。</p><p style=\"text-indent:24px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Arial\">Working Permit</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:24px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial\">Working permit </span>大概要一周左右的时间才能处理完成，到时候<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">ISO</span>就会发邮件通知大家到<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">ISO</span>去领<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">Working  Permit</span>了。<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">ISO</span>的办公楼在数学系斜对面，叫做<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">Hatcher Hall</span>。</p><p><span style=\"font-family:Arial\"> </span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:Arial\">2.<span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px\">  </span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:Arial\">   </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px\">社会保险号</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:Arial\">SSN</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px\">的申请</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:Arial\"> </span></strong></p><p>新生到校<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">orientation</span>得时候会填一些表格，包括<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">working permit</span>的申请，等<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">ISO </span>完成了你得<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">working permit</span>，你就可以拿着系里的介绍信，<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">working permit</span>，护照，<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">I20</span>等其他资料（能想到得都带上吧）到<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">social security office </span>去申请了，可以坐<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">ICC</span>的<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">shuttle</span>去，要注意查收<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">ICC</span>的邮件。<span style=\"font-family:Arial\"> </span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:Arial\"><br  /></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:Arial\">3.<span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px\">  </span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:Arial\">   </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:19px\">入学英文水平测试</span></strong></p><p>此次英文测试并不会影响你的奖学金及学生身份，所以不要担心。</p><p>英文测试由两部分组成：</p><p><span style=\"font-family:Arial\">1. Michigan Test</span>：多项选择题<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">+</span>作文，一共<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">2</span>小时（本科生仅有选择题）。</p><p><span style=\"font-family:Arial\">2. Oral English</span>：<span style=\"font-family:Arial\">30 </span>分钟，一对一的口语测试，在新生<span style=\"font-family:Arial\"> orientation</span>时预约时间。</p><p><span style=\"font-family:Arial\"> </span></p><p>英文写作课及口语课将根据你的考试成绩为你安排，如果你考的非常</p><p>好，可以不上这两种英文课，不过就经验而谈，一般中国学生都是要上英文</p><p>课及口语课的。如果你觉得你的英文水平比考试成绩好，在开课的第一周，</p><p>每个人还有第二次机会，如果这次表现的好，还是可以免上英文课的（仅限研究生）。</p><p><br  /></p>","url":"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIwMjAwNDUxMg==&mid=210127661&idx=1&sn=86b809dc291cd23982d6026f836240fd#rd","thumb_media_id":"OkZEQ4EpVVS2JPd1-lu13cvkllQ8EjECXRWhoYpBKfY","thumb_url":"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/cGcYqtanUyuRFt8YtqWZPXCf1CCeqWqTSZNQAaicTav7zt5etEib0Jiab2kLtGdk2KqQhvqRGcRNAZoribYk1ZdkGw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg","update_time":"2015-07-10T14:39:26.000Z","media_id":"OkZEQ4EpVVS2JPd1-lu13UuMWCMqDtIg6yMg71wk5AY","createdAt":"2021-03-26T18:57:49.018Z","updatedAt":"2021-03-26T18:57:51.569Z","__v":0,"thumb_media":{"_id":"605e2eaf14f2894457a29cde","name":"2021226-17495-6x6mjn","alternativeText":null,"caption":null,"hash":"2021226_17495_6x6mjn_6f0a93de44","ext":".jpeg","mime":"image/jpeg","size":520.29,"width":1729,"height":2700,"url":"/uploads/2021226_17495_6x6mjn_6f0a93de44.jpeg","formats":{"thumbnail":{"hash":"thumbnail_2021226_17495_6x6mjn_6f0a93de44","ext":".jpeg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":100,"height":156,"size":4.13,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/thumbnail_2021226_17495_6x6mjn_6f0a93de44.jpeg"},"large":{"hash":"large_2021226_17495_6x6mjn_6f0a93de44","ext":".jpeg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":640,"height":1000,"size":99.14,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/large_2021226_17495_6x6mjn_6f0a93de44.jpeg"},"medium":{"hash":"medium_2021226_17495_6x6mjn_6f0a93de44","ext":".jpeg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":480,"height":750,"size":59.98,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/medium_2021226_17495_6x6mjn_6f0a93de44.jpeg"},"small":{"hash":"small_2021226_17495_6x6mjn_6f0a93de44","ext":".jpeg","mime":"image/jpeg","width":320,"height":500,"size":28.81,"path":null,"url":"/uploads/small_2021226_17495_6x6mjn_6f0a93de44.jpeg"}},"provider":"local","related":["605e2ead14f2894457a29cdd"],"createdAt":"2021-03-26T18:57:51.564Z","updatedAt":"2021-03-26T18:57:51.568Z","__v":0,"id":"605e2eaf14f2894457a29cde"},"id":"605e2ead14f2894457a29cdd"}},"__N_SSG":true}